    },
    {
      "num": "02 · the move",
      "heading": "Bring the ask with the problem",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">Say what is happening, why it matters, what you tried, and what help would change the outcome. That lets your manager use their different tools.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "file": "manager-update.md",
          "code": "Risk: checkout migration misses beta date\nCause: product copy not approved\nTried: async thread, design review\nAsk: decision owner by Wednesday",
          "caption": "A clear ask is easier to act on than a weather report."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "num": "03 · the check",
      "heading": "Escalate early enough to matter",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">Escalation is not failure. It is routing a problem to the level where it can be solved before it becomes drama.</p>"
        },
